{"tid":52593,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[劣改][蟈蜻] 霧(霾)之傳 (原曲：霧之戀)","createTime":"2016-12-24T07:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T13:10:17.000Z","uid":34701,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60e5b7fb2baea5657a54e3f62c9d794a65b7d4e1","tid":52593,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:38:22.000Z","msg":"街邊的樓睇不清　海邊的景睇不清<br />\n白日白霧上演不停<br />\n似要悄悄告訴這世界　大陸實在是幻像<br />\n你要看　始終看不清<br />\n<br />\n枱面的卷睇不清　枱底出貓睇不清<br />\n戶外撥著霧　考生失明<br />\n似要暗暗告訴我與你　個肺也會像霧幻<br />\n轉眼間會花晒<br />\n<br />\n政協說冇有錯　再說算你有錯<br />\n大陸現實是永不改變<br />\n告訴我說要閉氣　我怕終於一天<br />\n再也不不會再唞氣<br />\n<br />\n濃霧起暗暗蓋掩身邊美<br />\n在霧裡　病情幻化不定<br />\n無法記起以往那刻　氧怎闖進我身裡<br />\n還是戴著罩　全日戴著罩　去當做養生<br />\n<br />\n每次我外出企　每次我換親氣<br />\n我那口腔中　也都有霧<br />\n每次我外出企　每次我換親氣<br />\n我那肺泡都變老<br />\n<br />\n歡迎畀意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e5c2fd656c051025254cb68ab5ef079343ce45","tid":52593,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cacef1bd3bb2f782e8f7591ddf2bef947593649","tid":52593,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b982e1d44d913ef161bb6b3298f48484630a4c0e","tid":52593,"uid":1848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:10:21.000Z","msg":"就咁睇九成冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實際唱落再比意見你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0db01055f12bd5441dbc5403dfc1e3901ade81","tid":52593,"uid":34701,"like":0,"disl