52593,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:20:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果可以再改多d會更有個人特色，唔好俾佢本來個版本規限住，搞到每句淨係改得嗰一兩隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前聽林夕講過話如果一首改歌只係改少少歌詞，已經可以帶出另一種意思，先係高質嘅改詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我都係玩下啫，始終唔夠啲高手嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1561649456ef19699cbbfeabfead0eb80ca129","tid":52593,"uid":1848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T08:19:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://app.box.com/s/n1245dyao4feda480uxdnuffm07sroxp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp.box.com%2Fs%2Fn1245dyao4feda480uxdnuffm07sroxp&d=0j3e67mZ5s9ptsw%2B7DTk0GN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=028e5cdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://app.box.com/s/n1245dyao4feda480uxdnuffm07sroxp</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bdf1e7f6c86434c100e6ed279f311aa65eba4b0","tid":52593,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T08:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://app.box.com/s/n1245dyao4feda480uxdnuffm07sroxp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp.box.com%2Fs%2Fn1245dyao4feda480uxdnuffm07sroxp&d=0j3e67mZ5s9ptsw%2B7DTk0GN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=028e5cdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://app.box.com/s/n1245dyao4feda480uxdnuffm07sroxp</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正"}]}